e: 14px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">只记取你</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">眉宇轻扬，疼握我手</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">/</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">爱过，不说后悔</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">-</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">《爱你，护你安好》</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">-</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">夜太深</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">深到我勾勒不出眼泪的湿度</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">念太薄</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">薄得我仅能载起此刻繁华</p><p s